{"tid":1361274,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼琴女神慶生大開「酒池肉林」趴　揪猛男上下全脫玩泡泡","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:30:14.000Z","uid":81228,"like":36,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"43e3aa653afd5b57b10c19aef11b1b3a14cb1013","tid":1361274,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞女鋼琴家李元玲是國際著名鋼琴家李雲迪的愛徒，除了有著精湛琴技外還是名專業的芭蕾舞者，多才多藝的她也是健身愛好者，體脂肪甚至只有12。日前李元玲迎來30歲生日，找來2、30名友人大開慶生派對，當天照片曝光後，超狂的生日派對規格和李元玲的火辣身材掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035103-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035103-XXL.jpg&h=d3112f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲是健身愛好者，體脂肪甚至只有12。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<br />\n李元玲有著甜美外表和火辣身材，也時常透過社群網站分享美照，IG追蹤人數突破百萬，近日她在IG分享30歲慶生派對的影片和照片，只見派對現場做為壽星的她穿著爆乳比基尼和小熱褲，展現小蠻腰和一雙修長美腿，傲人上圍更是呼之欲出，性感指數爆表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035102-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035102-XXL.jpg&h=48b463ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲李元玲在生日派對上和友人同歡。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035100-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035100-XXL.jpg&h=a48ffd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片中，李元玲開心地切著兩個生日蛋糕，蛋糕上頭還插著仙女棒，點燃後不斷冒出絢爛煙火，現場更有著滿坑滿谷的美酒佳餚，還找來師傅現做日本料理，「酒池肉林」等級的高規格豪華慶生派對令人大開眼界，而主角李元玲時而和姊妹開心聊天，時而被猛男圍繞，氣氛相當熱烈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035099-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035099-XXL.jpg&h=23bc2c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲李元玲穿著清涼，最後甚至僅穿著黑色蕾絲內褲大玩泡泡浴。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035101-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035101-XXL.jpg&h=3f2ab11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了美食美酒之外，派對現場還有戶外泡泡泳池供眾人同歡，李元玲更大方脫掉熱褲，僅穿著一件黑色蕾絲內褲入鏡，養眼畫面引人遐想，粉絲除了獻上生日祝福外，也忍不住直呼「太狂了！」、「不愧是當紅的大馬女神」、「希望我也在那！」<br />\n<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=574847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D574847&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Gipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=65192e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D574847&h=a6830220\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=574847</a>"},{"pid":"ad76fa4388582fe3d7239962c1efa348d1cdc2b5","tid":1361274,"uid":143093,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"咁都鋼琴女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王羽佳先係鋼琴女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ed248bc43c1556b31eb709aad793eb5d1d07f7","tid":1361274,"uid":138138,"like":62,"dislike":7,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"p圖p到仆街喎，真人差咁多既"},{"pid":"f2088d702b60d6c3721d21d2871f4c232d91d9e7","tid":1361274,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad76fa4388582fe3d7239962c1efa348d1cdc2b5","tid":1361274,"uid":143093,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"咁都鋼琴女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王羽佳先係鋼琴女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"Yuja 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢件都好掂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-eJU41Tc7l8\" data-sr-url=\"h