 />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHSwKxN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHSwKxN.png&h=5635a962&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"之前見到都unfollow左<br />\n呢類人係極度自我中心既完美主義者"},{"pid":"f86d71deb4e1ed5cc505a1be3b9268b41907b4ff","tid":1361274,"uid":154631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24cef3ee7179d84c502c03b7ed4c729cca68189d","tid":1361274,"uid":161462,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e3aa653afd5b57b10c19aef11b1b3a14cb1013","tid":1361274,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞女鋼琴家李元玲是國際著名鋼琴家李雲迪的愛徒，除了有著精湛琴技外還是名專業的芭蕾舞者，多才多藝的她也是健身愛好者，體脂肪甚至只有12。日前李元玲迎來30歲生日，找來2、30名友人大開慶生派對，當天照片曝光後，超狂的生日派對規格和李元玲的火辣身材掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035103-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035103-XXL.jpg&h=d3112f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲是健身愛好者，體脂肪甚至只有12。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<br />\n李元玲有著甜美外表和火辣身材，也時常透過社群網站分享美照，IG追蹤人數突破百萬，近日她在IG分享30歲慶生派對的影片和照片，只見派對現場做為壽星的她穿著爆乳比基尼和小熱褲，展現小蠻腰和一雙修長美腿，傲人上圍更是呼之欲出，性感指數爆表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035102-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035102-XXL.jpg&h=48b463ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲李元玲在生日派對上和友人同歡。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035100-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035100-XXL.jpg&h=a48ffd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影片中，李元玲開心地切著兩個生日蛋糕，蛋糕上頭還插著仙女棒，點燃後不斷冒出絢爛煙火，現場更有著滿坑滿谷的美酒佳餚，還找來師傅現做日本料理，「酒池肉林」等級的高規格豪華慶生派對令人大開眼界，而主角李元玲時而和姊妹開心聊天，時而被猛男圍繞，氣氛相當熱烈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035099-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035099-XXL.jpg&h=23bc2c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲李元玲穿著清涼，最後甚至僅穿著黑色蕾絲內褲大玩泡泡浴。（圖／翻攝自李元玲IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/23/2035101-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F23%2F2035101-XXL.jpg&h=3f2ab11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了美食美酒之外，派對現場還有戶外泡泡泳池供眾人同歡，李元玲更大方脫掉熱褲，僅穿著一件黑色蕾絲內褲入鏡，養眼畫面引人遐想，粉絲除了獻上生日祝福外，也忍不住直呼「太狂了！」、「不愧是當紅的大馬女神」、「希望我也在那！」<br />\n<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=574847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D574847&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0Gipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=65192e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D574847&h=a6830220\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=574847</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"咪又係會食飯會柯屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"會屙屎好啊<br />\n起馬可以有入有出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0d1f44c7a78081096ec22b96873991a9dc18a2","tid":1361274,"uid":5151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:28:11.000Z","msg":"擺明有sugar daddy"},{"pid":"8e82074e67da7a485d71dd1123817fe2382d06f3","tid":1361274,"uid":65911,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:29:19.000Z","msg":"佢對微波谷到咁都係得個少少  好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ad99899d0cac9417a4895674c26671082cb113","tid":1361274,"uid":267348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人體脂12 應該好難黎M"},{"pid":"0a0e8be0509686a919d148e66714a64c5fcac8d3","tid":1361274,"uid":71140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"re